<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كِتَابًا}</span> ... مَكْتُوبًا مَفْرُوضًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّوْقُوتًا}</span> ... مُحَدَّدًا فِي أَوْقَاتٍ مَعْلُومَةٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
