<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَخْتَانُونَ}</span> ... يَخُونُونَ أَنْفُسَهُمْ بِالْمعَصِيَةِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَوَّانًا}</span> ... عَظِيمَ الخِيَانَةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُبَيِّتُونَ}</span> ... يُدَبِّرُونَ لَيْلًا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَّجْوَاهُمْ}</span> ... حَدِيثَهُمْ سِرًّا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُشَاقِقِ}</span> ... يُخَالِفْ عِنَادًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُوَلِّهِ مَا تَوَلَّى}</span> ... نَتْرُكْهُ، وَمَا تَوَجَّهَ إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
